These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-1::.
There 2 different types of food: apple, peach
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, begonia
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, cycling
2 different games are played: go, backgammon
2 different pets are kept: ferret, goat
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, van
1. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person eating peach is on the far right##1
4. the person playing go is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Food      | apple       | peach    |
| Flower           | begonia | bellflower |
| Sport   | cycling     | water-polo   |
| Game   | backgammon  | go     |
| Pet           | goat       | ferret     |
| Transport     | roller     | van        |

