.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: coral, chestnut
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, alhambra
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, crime
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, pop
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, sunflower
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, june
1. the fan of pop is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person who likes chestnut is the fan of pop##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Color      | coral        | chestnut   |
| Cigar         | alhambra | pall-mall |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | crime   |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | pop     |
| Flower           | sunflower        | amaryllis    |
| Birthday     | august  | june    |

