The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, parkour
1. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the person playing domino is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
3. the nurse is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |
| Food          | pepper    | avocado      |
| Cigar         | game   | montecristo       |
